    "page": "notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_49",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_49_3",
    "text": "What are those?(那是什么?) what co lours do thoy have?(它有哪些颜色?)",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
