  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_49_4",
    "text": "10.相互代词：表示相互关策的词叫相互伐词。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10986964618249534,
      0.3893280632411067,
      0.638733705772812,
      0.4163372859025033
    ],
    "page": "notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_49",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_49_5",
    "text": "each other，oeanother是相互代词，译为”互相”，可以通用。each other表示两者之间，而one another表示许多人之间。他们有所有格形式： each other's, one another's.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10707635009310987,
      0.42160737812911725,
      0.9199255121042831,
      0.5079051383399209
    ],
    "page": "notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_49",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_49_6",
    "text": "yo: We must help each other when we are in trouble. (我们身处闲境时要互相帮助.)",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.13687150837988826,
      0.5158102766798419,
